  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add chopped onion and minced garlic, sauté for about 3 minutes until softened.",
    "Stir in tomato paste, cumin seeds, coriander seeds, salt, and pepper. Cook for another minute to meld flavors.",
    "Gradually add water or chicken broth while stirring continuously to prevent lumps from forming.",
    "Bring the sauce to a simmer then reduce heat to low.",
    "Add egg noodles and cook until tender yet still al dente (about 10-12 minutes), tossing occasionally.",
    "Remove from heat and let sit for a few minutes before serving."
  ],
